{"tid":465563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警荷槍實彈嚴陣戒備     原來係大學生拍戲惹虛驚","createTime":"2017-11-11T16:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T16:59:07.000Z","uid":48093,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa90fdd923f6e0b666212e40ff4d5eed651430c","tid":465563,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171111/large/1510415595_e56b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171111%2Flarge%2F1510415595_e56b.jpg&h=09665c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【00:06】大批EU趕往現場上樓調查，發現是虛驚一場，涉事男子報稱大學生，事發時正在單位內拍戲，警方又撿獲懷疑玩具槍，正調查其真偽。<br />\n【23:48】受事件影響，港鐵職員將太子港鐵站B2出口暫時拉閘封閉。<br />\n<br />\n星期六晚上10時許，警方接到一名保安員報案，指太子聯合廣場樓上有住戶被人行劫，警方隨即趕往現場，多名戴頭盔、身穿避彈衣的警員手持盾頭到場，並封鎖大廈所有的出入口，又向途人查問，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後發現，有住戶覺得鄰居被人打劫，於是通知保安員，保安立即報警指有人持槍行劫。大批EU趕往現場上樓調查，終於鎖定7樓一單位並尋持到涉事人士，原來發現是虛驚一場。涉事男子報稱大學生，事發時正在單位內拍戲，警方又撿獲懷疑玩具槍，正調查其真偽。"},{"pid":"abaf0f6c300bbabb63f172773eca0e667e2f0cbf","tid":465563,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"笑"},{"pid":"16b05eb18b522c624cfc06892b89855b0fe2383a","tid":465563,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd42ecc623182e1f75394e562dd4ce9387e5c28","tid":465563,"uid":46151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:29:16.000Z","msg":"浪費警力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44203a64208fe60781214872b61ce51a7978b9ac","tid":465563,"uid":131323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:29:58.000Z","msg":"廢老浪費警力"},{"pid":"fae50f7df2f97e9df51ab82430836355d9035